ly</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marc-minkowski/" rel="tag">Marc Minkowski</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marianne-crebassa/" rel="tag">Marianne Crebassa</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/maurice-ravel/" rel="tag">Maurice Ravel</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/silvia-mapelli/" rel="tag">Silvia Mapelli</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/stephanie-d%e2%80%99oustrac/" rel="tag">Stphanie dOustrac</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/vincent-le-texier/" rel="tag">Vincent Le Texier</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/yann-beuron/" rel="tag">Yann Beuron</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Agnese Vitali, Alla Samokhotova, Amor Lilia Perez Lopez, Anna Devin, Armelle Khourdoan, Barbara de Limbourg, Bruno Casoni, Carline Ginet, Chiara Tirotta, Davide Baronchelli, Delphine Haidan, Elissa Huber, Fatma Said, Florence Evrand, Giuseppe Bellanca, Jean-Luc Ballestra, Jean-Paul Fouchron, Jrme Varnier, laurent pelly, Marc Minkowski, Marianne Crebassa, Maurice Ravel, Opera lirica, Silvia Mapelli, Stphanie dOustrac, Vincent Le Texier, Yann Beuron"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e815c56665d91cc0feb9dea3e3c28ca4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/giordano-cavagnino-100x150.jpg" width="67" height="100" alt="Giordano Cavagnino" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Giordano Cavagnino"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i 